name: Dream Street Beauty Great Britain
description:
Dream Street Beauty Great Britain & Ireland has now franchised for the first year ever meaning that more heats have been added to target the most beautiful women nationwide, The event will fund-raise for Arthritis Research UK.

Dream Street Beauty has no weight, height or limits so any woman can enter as long as they are aged between 4 and 45! You can be married, Have Children or have no experience in pageantry at all.. This event has been created to help aspiring models reach their modelling dreams and higher.. Creating that platform!

The winner will receive the UK Crown & Title, 12 Month Model Contract, Become the Face of Dream Street UK, A Photo shoot in a luxury Log Cabin in Hereford with private Jacuzzi & Swimming Pool to be made into a Calender & Portfolio, Gift Bag full of Prizes! MORE TBC

Overall Titles:
*Dream Street England, Scotland & Wales
*Dream Street Great Britain 
*Charitable Queen. 

Side Titles:
* Dream Street Inspirational Beauty 
* Dream Street's Great British Supermodel 
* Dream Street's Natural Beauty 2013
* Directors Choice 2014
* Miss Photogenic 
* Miss Social Media Queen.
* Miss Community 
* Miss Outstanding Beauty.
* Miss Inked Beauty 2014 (Miss & Queen Only)

name: Training Academy - Portfolio Sessions
description:
Every Sunday in October in Birmingham City Center 

(Excluding 20th due to Birmingham Marathon this weekend date will be the 19th)

A different theme and location each week enables models to build up their confidence, Learn from professionals and finish the course with a strong portfolio.
